    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>A HAUNTING JOURNEY AT SEA</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>At Sea</i>, you play as Maris, a young child who finds himself trapped in a decaying ship - drifting through an endless, storm-tossed ocean. Isolated and surrounded by unsettling creatures, your survival depends on navigating the ship's eerie corridors, solving puzzles, and outsmarting your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/6221a32d1d28d2341af5642a8d887ad5.poster.avif?t=1750166673\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/6221a32d1d28d2341af5642a8d887ad5.webm?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/6221a32d1d28d2341af5642a8d887ad5.mp4?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>SURVIVE THE HORRORS</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ship isn’t just a setting - it’s a maze of treacherous obstacles and strange inhabitants. From flooded  rooms to towering masts, you'll need to explore every corner to uncover the ship's secrets. Each room offers a new challenge, but danger lurks in every shadow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/59b352142863ef348d0ee40d103b4b0e.poster.avif?t=1750166673\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/59b352142863ef348d0ee40d103b4b0e.webm?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/59b352142863ef348d0ee40d103b4b0e.mp4?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>OUTWIT DEADLY CREATURES</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ship is haunted by mysterious creatures, strange and terrifying beings that stalk the flooded halls. They may not see you, but they can hear you. Move quietly, hide in the shadows, and use your environment to avoid becoming their next victim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/49263aef61b34474d15e73e11ad61319.poster.avif?t=1750166673\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/49263aef61b34474d15e73e11ad61319.webm?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/49263aef61b34474d15e73e11ad61319.mp4?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>THE ISLAND ENTICES</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your only hope of escape is a distant island. But as you make your way closer, it becomes clear that the island may not be the sanctuary you hoped for. What awaits you there is covered in mystery and dread.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/fb69b5d3172b4adddaa78ad35d4e269f.poster.avif?t=1750166673\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/fb69b5d3172b4adddaa78ad35d4e269f.webm?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308380/extras/fb69b5d3172b4adddaa78ad35d4e269f.mp4?t=1750166673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Maris find freedom on the island, or does a greater danger await him?</p>",
